extendedInfo.description: Help a cute flying baby puke while collecting his magic milk bottles and avoiding dangerous clouds. As a newly born baby is too young to fly and sky realms is full of dangerous hurdles. You need to be quick as clouds are anxious about his flying and has headed out to end his journey!!Fall Fly & Puke is an entertaining FREE flying, falling & puking game, which will keep you engaged for hours! Collect as many milk bottles, banana and insect as possible to make a flying baby(hanging with his cute parachute) the happiest baby in the world. As you progress, you will discover many powerful power ups & bonuses to make his flying easier! Just be careful some obstacles like flying clouds will get in the way to block him.Once you accumulate a large amount of milk bottles, you will have the opportunity to rule the sky by magic puking on the flying bird. A highly entertaining and insanely addictive animated game includes cartoon-styled graphics with astonishing background. Three beautiful wonderland themes: shinning evening, dazzling night(full of twinkling & shinning stars) and fresh morning makes the game more interesting and entertaining. Designer has given the eye-pleasing and live flying situation by using perfect blend of baby colours like green, yellow, pink, red, black, white, purple etc.. with a funny character: sweet baby, crazy jungle monkey, flying penguin.  A fun and entertaining flying game will have you and your child (toddler or kid) laughing for hours.Features:â Super simple: One touch controls.â Advanced HD graphics with the eye-catching animations makes this a game that requires strategy, skill and dexterity to master.â Many quests to complete. Are you ready for an amazing top free game of falling, flying & puking baby?
